---
layout: base.njk
title: Admin Review Queue
description: "Admin review queue — I-PACE Owners' Advocacy Group."
permalink: /admin/review-queue/
---

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="page-header__eyebrow">Admin</p>
    <h1 class="page-header__title">Review Queue</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="container">

    <!-- Not logged in -->
    <div data-auth-gate>
      <div class="auth-gate">
        <div class="auth-gate__icon" aria-hidden="true">🔒</div>
        <h2 class="auth-gate__title">Sign in required</h2>
        <p class="auth-gate__body">You must be signed in to access admin pages.</p>
        <button class="btn btn--primary" type="button" data-identity-open="login">Sign in</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Logged in, no admin role -->
    <div data-admin-gate style="display:none;">
      <div class="auth-gate">
        <div class="auth-gate__icon" aria-hidden="true">⛔</div>
        <h2 class="auth-gate__title">Access restricted</h2>
        <p class="auth-gate__body">
          This page is for group administrators only. If you believe you should have admin access,
          please contact us.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--secondary">Contact us</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Admin content -->
    <div data-admin-content style="display:none;">
      <div class="callout callout--warning" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
        <span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚠️</span>
        <div class="callout__content">
          <p class="callout__title">Placeholder admin UI</p>
          <p>The admin review queue is a placeholder. Real submission review functionality will
          be implemented via Netlify Functions now that the first Join and vehicle-basics
          records are stored server-side.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom:0;"><strong>Security note:</strong> Frontend role-checking is
          not sufficient for real admin data access. All admin Netlify Functions must verify
          the Identity JWT server-side and confirm the admin role in <code>app_metadata.roles</code>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dashboard-panel">
        <div class="dashboard-panel__header">
          <h2 class="dashboard-panel__title">Pending review</h2>
          <span class="badge badge--warning">0 pending</span>
        </div>
        <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);">No submissions awaiting review. Once data collection begins, new submissions will appear here for verification.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: var(--space-6);">
        <h2>Admin navigation</h2>
        <div class="cluster">
          {% for item in navigation.admin %}
            <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="btn btn--secondary btn--sm">{{ item.label }}</a>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
